Workaround applied during verify:
  workspaces.browserbase_profile_id was already set to a stale Phase G.2
  Context (564581a2-…) from earlier loop iterations. My new code uses the
  workspace-level profile FIRST and only falls back to browser_sites when
  null — wrong priority. SQL:
    UPDATE workspaces SET browserbase_profile_id = NULL
     WHERE id = '139e7cdc-…';
  After nulling, the next run correctly picked the browser-sites Context.
  Deferred follow-up: invert worker lookup order so browser_sites > profile
  (requires worker rebuild + push). Tracked below.

